    "start": 693.911,
    "duration": 1.533
  },
  {
    "text": "By the way, that filming studio\nwas really pretty",
    "start": 695.446,
    "duration": 2.919
  },
  {
    "text": "It was the best filming studio so far",
    "start": 698.605,
    "duration": 2.714
  },
  {
    "text": "When we were filming the music video,\nMARK and DOYOUNG",
    "start": 701.548,
    "duration": 6.282
  },
  {
    "text": "Huh?",
    "start": 707.83,
    "duration": 0.562
  },
  {
    "text": "MARK came to support us\nand DOYOUNG sent us drinks",
    "start": 708.393,
    "duration": 4.318
  },
  {
    "text": "Did he send us drinks?",
    "start": 712.711,
    "duration": 1.007
  },
  {
    "text": "(That made us feel happy haha)",
    "start": 713.72,
    "duration": 1.356
  },
  {
    "text": "I didn't know",
    "start": 715.076,
    "duration": 1.494
  },
  {
    "text": "Really? What else did he send?",
    "start": 716.991,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "Drinks, coffee, and everything",
    "start": 718.488,
    "duration": 2.048
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, Starbucks",
    "start": 720.537,
    "duration": 0.971
  },
  {
    "text": "Did DOYOUNG send us all of those?",
    "start": 721.509,
    "duration": 2.147
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah",
    "start": 723.657,
    "duration": 0.795
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh really? I didn't know",
    "start": 724.893,
    "duration": 2.182
  },
  {
    "text": "So we had a chance to take\na look at our music video",
    "start": 727.076,
    "duration": 3.775
  },
  {
    "text": "As expected, each scene in which \nour members came out were all",
    "start": 730.852,
    "duration": 3.903
  },
  {
    "text": "literally very impressive",
    "start": 734.755,
    "duration": 2.004
  },
  {
    "text": "I realized there were a lot of highlights",
    "start": 736.759,
    "duration": 2.167
  },
  {
    "text": "Each member (had many highlights)",
    "start": 738.927,
    "duration": 1.018
  },
  {
    "text": "It brought many things to my mind as well",
    "start": 739.946,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "Right",
    "start": 741.307,
    "duration": 0.374
  },
  {
    "text": "All the music videos were great",
    "start": 741.681,
    "duration": 1.993
  },
  {
    "text": "but this music video \nis especially good",
    "start": 743.675,
    "duration": 1.733
  },
  {
    "text": "This music video shows \nhow much we've grown",
    "start": 745.41,
    "duration": 3.03
  },
  {
    "text": "so it felt very different \nin that way as well",
    "start": 748.441,
    "duration": 1.43
  },
  {
    "text": "I suggest that",
    "start": 749.871,
    "duration": 1.161
  },
  {
    "text": "after you watch this music video",
    "start": 751.032,
    "duration": 1.578
  },
  {
    "text": "you watch all the music videos \nstarting from Chewing Gum to this one",
    "start": 752.611,
    "duration": 3.413
  },
  {
    "text": "(Good suggestion)\nWow",
    "start": 756.026,
    "duration": 0.669
  },
  {
    "text": "It shows how we've grown",
    "start": 756.696,
    "duration": 1.75
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm not saying with an ulterior motive",
    "start": 758.906,
    "duration": 0.945
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll be able to see how \nNCT DREAM members have grown",
    "start": 759.852,
    "duration": 2.516
  },
  {
